com.datamelt.rules.core

Class ReferenceField

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.datamelt.rules.core.ReferenceField

  • public class ReferenceField
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines a reference field as it is used and output by the BusinessRulesMaintenance Tool. It basically defines one field of a row of fields from a record (e.g. a line from a CSV file). The field has a name and Java type assigned to it. The ruleengine will use this information to correctly process the value of the field.
    Author:
    uwe geercken
